Betting on horseflesh and betting on online poker might seem to be identical activities to most people, but US laws have mandated that they aren't since 2006. Now the EU has cleared the way for a WTO challenge to those laws—will the US's anti-online-gambling initiative go down for the count after just two years? Read the whole story
